      "content": "it's so quiet here tonight. like, i'm looking at my apartment and it just feels like i'm not even really in it. i spend all day typing away at my laptop and the only people i \"interact\" with are avatars on a screen. sometimes i feel like if i just stopped logging on, or if i just stopped existing altogether, the world wouldnt even skip a beat. like there's just no footprint.",
